545
00:26:05,689 --> 00:26:11,736
♪ And shelter me forever ♪

546
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:17,576
♪ That was a hard promise to keep ♪

547
00:26:17,659 --> 00:26:24,040
♪ I can't blame you for the bad weather ♪

548
00:26:24,124 --> 00:26:29,963
♪ After all that has been said and done ♪

549
00:26:30,046 --> 00:26:36,136
♪ I won't ask you where you're going ♪

550
00:26:36,219 --> 00:26:39,180
♪ Don't keep in touch ♪

551
00:26:39,264 --> 00:26:42,058
♪ I don't miss you much ♪

552
00:26:42,142 --> 00:26:48,481
♪ Except sometimes early in the morning ♪

553
00:26:48,565 --> 00:26:52,944
-♪ Now use your silver tongue… ♪
-Excuse me, sir.

554
00:26:53,028 --> 00:26:57,657
Can you head back downtown?
I want to go to L'Express.

555
00:26:57,741 --> 00:26:59,075
♪ …I'd like to know ♪

556
00:27:00,118 --> 00:27:03,121
♪ Did you ever believe ♪

557
00:27:03,622 --> 00:27:06,291
-♪ The lies that you told? ♪
-Thanks.

558
00:27:06,374 --> 00:27:12,547
♪ Did you earn the fool's gold
That you gave me? ♪

559
00:27:13,423 --> 00:27:15,717
[vocalizing]

560
00:27:24,601 --> 00:27:27,896
-♪ Did you ever believe… ♪
-Oh my God.

561
00:27:27,979 --> 00:27:30,690
♪ The lies that you told? ♪

562
00:27:30,774 --> 00:27:36,571
♪ Did you earn the fool's gold
That you gave me? ♪

563
00:27:36,655 --> 00:27:42,661
♪ Did you ever believe
The lies that you told? ♪

564
00:27:42,744 --> 00:27:49,668
♪ Did you earn the fool's gold
That you gave me? ♪

565
00:27:50,335 --> 00:27:53,004
Jesus Christ!
You scared the shit out of me!

566
00:27:54,255 --> 00:27:55,632
What are you doing here?

567
00:27:56,508 --> 00:27:57,342
I think…

568
00:27:59,344 --> 00:28:00,845
I think I made a mistake.

569
00:28:03,223 --> 00:28:05,225
["If You Love Me (Really Love Me)"
